---
description:
globs: frontend/*
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use best practices for writing clean Nuxt.js code
- Always use shadcn/ui components that are available in frontent/components/ui
- When writing .vue components, do not write imports for shadcn/ui components since these are auto-imported
- All links to pages in the app should use NuxtLink, not <a> tags unless linking to an external site
- For tables that require pagination, use the usePagination and PaginationControls component to keep code DRY